<a href="/wiki/File:Maxwell_sig.jpg" class="image" title="James Clerk Maxwell's signature"><img alt="James Clerk Maxwell's signature" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/96/Maxwell_sig.jpg/128px-Maxwell_sig.jpg" width="128" height="30" border="0" /></a></td>
